## Common Layout Mistakes

- DO NOT use arbitrary hex without design system reference
- DO NOT hardcode spacing values — use Tailwind spacing scale
- DO NOT forget transitions on interactive elements
- DO NOT use `pt-[12px]` for Settings (use `pt-[20px]`)
- DO use CSS variables from theme.css
- DO provide hover states for all interactive elements
- DO ensure mobile responsiveness
- DO use edge-to-edge separators with `calc(100%+64px)` pattern in padded pages **where a full-bleed rule is intended** — not around the Payments / Settlements / Payment Pages filter rows (those use the inset `#fafafa` card).
